FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776423773
OL,3,C'How I made upskirting a crime'
OL,5,F"Sexist comments, dismissive
OL,6,Fattitudes, all those behaviours that
OL,7,Fwe see at the bottom of the pyramid of
OL,8,Fsexual violence."
OL,10,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,11,FITVX
